    <section id="id8475827">
      <title>the meaning of the word ‘energy’</title>
      <section id="id6744221">
        <title>ENERGY AND CHANGE</title>
        <para id="id8596156">What is the meaning of the word energy? If we consult a dictionary, it is defined as <emphasis effect="bold">the power to operate or act or the capacity of a body or system to do work</emphasis>.</para>
        <section id="id10331628">
          <title>Activity:</title>
          <para id="para-id10331628">
